    public abstract class LayerBase
extends RegisteredObjectBase
implements Layer
    The basic type of Neural Network LayerBase supporting the backpropigation model of learning. In general, these components define differentiable functions and the accompanying derivatives. The interface is designed to support composability; see DAGNetwork for composition details.
